{"tid":2079210,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"東歐共產政權民主化對香港嘅啟示","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T17:11:50.000Z","uid":40431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"156d86a7a320b05974537b31f6d42d1b82db814e","tid":2079210,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題，可能有睇開明居正嘅連登仔覺得好熟，因為佢喺三個唔同嘅節目講過相近嘅題目**：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zlfZCrxeiCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzlfZCrxeiCg&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=319672b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zlfZCrxeiCg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係我想講有兩個共通點佢冇提到，但係好啱用喺而家嘅香港人身上：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>1. 外力可以製造一個有利嘅環境</strong></span><br />\n當年係冷戰，今年係美中之間嘅新冷戰，範圍包括經濟戰、關稅戰、科技戰、意識形態戰<br />\n一定程度上都會對共產政權造成不穩同壓力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>2. 最終共產政權必定係由人民自己推倒</strong></span><br />\n唔一定有反對派嘅存在，唔一定係武力革命，但係最後迫使共產政權倒台嘅都係人民而唔係外國<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>希望香港人了解呢兩點，外國無論點幫、幫幾多都好，最後要贏一定要靠自己。嚟緊日子可能會唔好過，但係我哋要堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n**明居正提到嘅共通點<br />\n1. 中產階層唔係必須<br />\n2. 反對黨派唔係必須<br />\n3. 速度可以好快，東歐民主化平均時間只係一至三年<br />\n4. 共產黨會出現退黨潮<br />\n5. 軍隊短期內可能會鎮壓，之後會轉趨消極甚至倒戈<br />\n6. 流血比想像中少，只有南斯拉夫發展成內戰<br />\n7. 共產政權倒台後社會變得穩定<br />\n8. 經濟短期內下降，四五年後回復原本水平，之後再上升超越原有水平<br />\n9. 出現自由組黨、選舉、建立國會"},{"pid":"4fe4dd0e1e4a82ab1b3e0a024a40389e9c10665b","tid":2079210,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ea75789f17c0ba94903e33e8a58f689e17357d","tid":2079210,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c064240d19dad45974a5b8a3912819527c5f89d6","tid":2079210,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"香港人要靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b08a292666c6432fd7b67ec1d5f25e4e524ea6b","tid":2079210,"uid":132189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇班狗就知冇可能"},{"pid":"d13705a28407f45c7750dfa308e7a265f6ce7de4","tid":2079210,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"由自由做個part認同<br />\n但5千年打仗歷史話你知<br />\n唔打唔鬆化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6c672beffcd919f9dd425be86997ae156e6913","tid":2079210,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d13705a28407f45c7750dfa308e7a265f6ce7de4","tid":2079210,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"由自由做個part認同<br />\n但5千年打仗歷史話你知<br />\n唔打唔鬆化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">己</span>"},{"pid":"4cd1cb9bef3bb77641dcb799b42a7785a171aabb","tid":2079210,"uid":99172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"第2點 最終共產政權必定係由人民自己推倒<br />\n係冇錯<br />\n但要知道我地面對嘅係中共 即係要靠中國人去推倒<br />\n不過班支人有排都唔識醒<br />\n其實民主建設中國呢個strategy係make sense <br />\n只不過之前個廿年浪費咗機會<br />\n當然好大原因亦係中共啲防火牆搞到資訊唔流通<br />\n所以我唔求滅共 鎖國就夠喇<br />\n不過唔該放番香港出黎"},{"pid":"6209cb5251bfaffdec54dd6f25a4ec7ac4cf62b2","tid":2079210,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c064240d19dad45974a5b8a3912819527c5f89d6","tid":2079210,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dis